    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I don't know what your exact problem is, but if you're receiving XML and want to return JSON (or something) you could also look at JAX-B. This is a standard for marshalling/unmarshalling Java POJO's to XML and/or Json. There are multiple libraries that implement JAX-B, for example Apache's CXF.</p>\n"
