      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "It&#39;s not clear to me how that solves the problem.  Do you just make everything an array instead of an object then?  E.g., if I have the XML <code>&lt;results&gt;&lt;result&gt;&lt;value&gt;1&lt;&#47;value&gt;&lt;&#47;result&gt;&lt;&#47;results&gt;</code>, would it generate  <code>{ &quot;results&quot; : { &quot;result&quot; : { &quot;value&quot; : &quot;1&quot; } } }</code>  or   <code>{ &quot;results&quot; : [ { &quot;result&quot; : { &quot;value&quot; : &quot;1&quot; } } ] }</code>"
