      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "There is something that we expect it to be an array. The problem arises when this array has only 1 element , making it an object for the xml-to-json converter. So , as we expect this to be an array for even a single element , we check and convert it to an array , making sure we have an array where we expect an array."
