      "body" : "If you have a valid dtd file for the xml snippet, then you can easily convert xml to json and json to xml using the open source eclipse link jar. Detailed sample JAVA project can be found here: <a href=\"http://www.cubicrace.com/2015/06/How-to-convert-XML-to-JSON-format.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">cubicrace.com/2015/06/How-to-convert-XML-to-JSON-format.html</a>"
